data.description: Indulge in luxury with this 4BR, 3 Bath home featuring an open floor plan, formal dining, designated office space and 4 car tandem 915 sqft garage!! The kitchen boasts a vented gas cooktop, island, pullout drawers, glass doors, and a large pantry. Breakfast bar seating. Custom trim, recessed lighting, and granite in all baths. Primary bedroom has new carpet, patio access, fabulous ensuite and enormous 8X13 walk in closet. Large covered front porch, substantial sized enclosed back porch and a cement patio with a gazebo awaits. 4 car tandem garage offers two drop-downs for attic storage. Flag pole adds a patriotic touch. Close to Madison shopping, and dining and quick access to highway!
